trade imbalance 
in the latest round of trade talks last week japan suggested 
the united states raise taxes wean itself from energywasting cars 
and limit the use of credit cards the mass circulation newspaper 
yomiuri shimbun reported 
the suggestions were among 80 japanese proposals for cutting the 
