testing of the longplanned tv marti began on channel 13 at 145 
am est in havana viewers saw a test pattern strong and 
clear 
two hours later came videos from mtv dubbed in spanish the 
world series tape the pittsburgh pirates beat the baltimore 
orioles in seven games and an episode of kate and allie the 
