minutes into the transmission in downtown havana and that viewers 
in outlying areas had few problems during the fivehour test 
cuban authorities have warned that the beginning of these 
transmissions may form part of a larger maneuver and washington may 
be looking for a pretext to unleash military aggression the 
cuban government news agency prensa latina said 
in panama the commander of us military forces in latin 
