the battle over jurisdiction of the industry stems in part from 
the governments investigation of illegal trading practices at the 
merc and board of trade fortyeight people mostly traders have 
been indicted in the probe prompting criticism that the cftc has 
been lax in policing the exchanges 
the turf battle also is rooted in the belief among some experts 
